    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until the veg has softened and the fish is cooked through – this is your <strong>fiery coconut hake en papillote and vegetables</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
