      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>fiery coconut hake</strong> <strong>en papillote</strong> <strong>and</strong> <strong>vegetables</strong> over the <strong>fragrant</strong> <strong>rice</strong></p><p>Pour the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>fiery coconut sauce</strong> from the parcels over the fish and vegetables</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> remaining chilli rounds </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
